  <name>Pinba Engine (MySQL 8.0)</name>
  <summary>Pinba storage engine plugin built for MySQL 8.0</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      This package provides ha_pinba.so compiled against MySQL 8.0 server
      headers. Pinba is a MySQL storage engine that collects and processes PHP
      runtime statistics sent over UDP by the Pinba PHP extension.
    </p>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.xolegator">
